# HeshbonAI Website — Cursor Rules

## What is HeshbonAI?

HeshbonAI automates client follow-up, document collection, and status tracking through WhatsApp for Israeli CPA firms. The assistant operates as a firm-branded persona (e.g., "Maya from Cohen & Co.") — clients never know it's automated.

- **HeshbonAI** = the company/business entity
- **John** = the AI assistant product (deployed per CPA firm when customers sign up)

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Astro (static site generator)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS with custom color palette (see tailwind.config.mjs)
- **Fonts:** Inter + Heebo (Hebrew) + JetBrains Mono (data)
- **Hosting:** Vercel (manual deploy: `npx vercel --prod --yes`)
- **No backend** — static site only

## Key Files

- `src/components/` — All page sections as Astro components
- `src/pages/` — Routes: index, pricing, how-it-works, about, contact
- `src/styles/global.css` — Base styles + component classes (.btn-primary, .card, etc.)
- `src/layouts/Layout.astro` — Base layout with SEO schema markup
- `tailwind.config.mjs` — Custom color palette
- `docs/` — All business docs (branding, product, competitors, prospects, website copy specs)

## Design System

### Colors (from tailwind.config.mjs)
- Background: Deep Navy `#0A1628`
- Surface/Cards: Slate Navy `#111C30`
- Primary Accent: Electric Blue `#2D7FF9`
- Text Primary: Off White `#E8ECF1`
- Text Secondary: Cool Gray `#8A95A8`
- Borders: `#263247`
- Success: `#00D68F` | Warning: `#FFB020` | Error: `#FF4D4F`
- WhatsApp: `#25D366`

### Component Classes (global.css)
- `.btn-primary` — Electric blue CTA button
- `.btn-secondary` — Bordered outline button
- `.section-label` — Blue uppercase label above section headings
- `.card` — Navy card with border and hover lift

## Content Rules — MUST FOLLOW

- Never say "bot" or "chatbot" — always "assistant"
- Never use AI hype language ("revolutionary," "game-changing")
- The CPA is the hero, HeshbonAI is the tool
- Short sentences, direct, outcome-focused
- Firm-branded assistant model: "Maya from [Firm Name]"
- No "free trial" — there is no free trial
- No "demo" page — use /contact instead
- CTAs say "Get Started" and link to /contact
- May have onboarding fee
- All prices excl. VAT

